title: The Fugitive S02E23 The Survivors DivX
description:
The Fugitive
S02E23
The Survivors


* One of 15 episodes from Season Two which have not been released on DVD
* Remastered audio and video from VHS
* Original music, not a synthesized replacement track
* With introduction by Barry Morse
* Includes a rare David Janssen network promo for Season Two of The Fugitive!

Original Air Date: 2 March 1965

Kimble (David Janssen) is spotted by a policeman when he returns to his wife's home town to help his bankrupt father-in-law.
Terry: Louise Sorel. Ed: Lloyd Gough. Edith: Ruth White.
